{"tid":614106,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[轟]牙朗應唔應該轉型？","createTime":"2018-04-02T08:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T03:48:19.000Z","uid":20134,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"49a62ae41983b6352f2605ab1f9bb3c8bf37b300","tid":614106,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"相信經過琴晚個場波大家都知道干地季尾走梗<br />\n如果下季係吐曹/sarri 教既話好大機會唔會再用343 <br />\n而改用翻433/4231 兩翼側擊<br />\n<br />\n牙朗雖然有極高體能 可以全場跑 助攻助守<br />\n但係佢速度之低有目共睹啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上佢一直都係打翼衛位置，如果轉翻做4後衛，佢防守慣性可能會令到整條防線崩潰（以往都係雞曉、老迪加幫佢包位先比較輕鬆）<br />\n<br />\n所以係4後衛體系中未必容納到佢<br />\n我就覺得應該要善用牙朗 身高、罰球遠射長傳、體能好、進攻意識強等等既優勢去改造成為一個b2b 左中場或者防中<br />\n<br />\n係YouTube 球王片入面見到牙朗上季其實係左邊禁區頂插上/遠射都有好大威脅，仲有中路靠左位置向前送長傳既能力，再加上無限體能<br />\n相信同kant&eacute; 一齊打中場會好過 巴膠/法比是但一個拍擋，再加一個靈活既攻擊中場(hazard out, Isco in?) 再買多個岀到波既翼，下季應該會爬翻上前四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送上上季球王片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/meq63CGvNSI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fmeq63CGvNSI&d=oJJwycnxtbbIxqRg37QJgaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=f11532ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/meq63CGvNSI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係好識波，屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3cc4bef53d7fe544bd47f1c425a3059b57277a","tid":614106,"uid":31151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"佢的確唔岩打左閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3e039f7d6889d2bd366a5e02c8c771723173b0","tid":614106,"uid":20134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢的確唔岩打左閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好鍾意佢，唔想第時轉4後衛冇得岀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc3331cc9f2f7f72e51ca118bef1c06ae1eee86","tid":614106,"uid":20134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"而且覺得全隊得佢同azp 有鐵血既感覺<br />\n真心希望佢地長留車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6011a5eda173090fff49f1b5852e1d6648272ede","tid":614106,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e429bb74296728d62a09ee0e34b4dad7653d83","tid":614106,"uid":136369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:19:26.000Z","msg":"講真 干地用M朗踢正選都係因為佢有罰球(英超罰球黎講佢實有頭3) <br />\n<br />\n如果佢無罰球Emerson應該係正選左閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151d8c3dcc624163d54b7ae1aa047ed22d8de73a","tid":614106,"uid":54025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"佢有速度佢就已經係世界第1左閘<br />\n<br />\n就唔會踢車仔了"},{"pid":"7b993b5fb1de73a2813fb5ac9d6e7be52c44f483","tid":614106,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 干地用M朗踢正選都係因為佢有罰球(英超罰球黎講佢實有頭3) <br />\n<br />\n如果佢無罰球Emerson應該係正選左閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴日emerson 標波好快，見佢踢波起碼叫有新氣象，將來應該會愈踢愈好<br />\n所以好驚新教練唔用朗囝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1ddc14b6350b3ed911a6c18964320529eec2a5","tid":614106,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢有速度佢就已經係世界第1左閘<br />\n<br />\n就唔會踢車仔了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class